NAME
    Log::ger::For::Builtins - Add logging to Perl builtins

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of Log::ger::For::Builtins (from
    Perl distribution Log-ger-For-Builtins), released on 2020-03-14.

SYNOPSIS
     use Log::ger::For::Builtins qw(
         readpipe
         rename
         system
     );

DESCRIPTION
    This module exports wrappers for Perl builtins with added logging.
    Logging is produced using Log::ger at the trace level and can be seen by
    using one of output plugins e.g. Log::ger::Output::Screen.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Log-ger-For-Builtins>.

